Students Social Media Addiction - Programming in Data Science IA Final Project

I showed how to perform data analysis on a dataset regarding a survey done towards students around the world about how much they use social media in everyday life. I used Google Colab and R language to perform data analysis such as data cleaning, data summarization and visualization to come up with the conclusion that among students, high school students are the most susceptible towards social media addiction as they spend the most time in a day to browse social media, hence feeling that their academic performance and mental health are worsened.

國民年金基金永續投資趨勢分析

透過這 6 分鐘的分析，我們不只學到了如何用程式碼解決中文亂碼，更看見了國家基金的轉型。
數據視覺化的目的，是為了讓政府的運作更加透明。當我們能親手繪製出這條「永續曲線」時，我們對社會保險的未來就多了一份掌握。
未來的研究方向，我們可以嘗試將「投資比例」與「基金收益率」進行交叉對比，看看永續投資是否真的能像學術界所說的，在降低風險的同時，也帶來穩定的長期回報。
